OL,3,C'Tragic and devastating accident':
OL,4,CWoman killed by falling tree branch
OL,6,FA woman died after a tree branch fell
OL,7,Fon her, in a "tragic and devastating
OL,8,Faccident", an inquest has heard.
OL,10,FJen Higgins and her husband Gawen were
OL,11,Fon a walk in West Didsbury,
OL,12,FManchester, in August 2025, when they
OL,13,Fwere hit by a branch, falling from a
OL,14,Ftree in a private property.
OL,16,FMr Higgins described a "large cracking
OL,17,Fnoise" before they were hit by the
OL,18,Fbranch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
