OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775848268
OL,3,C'Tragic and devastating accident':
OL,4,CWoman killed by falling tree branch
OL,6,FThe inquest, in Manchester, was told
OL,7,Fan off duty nurse started
OL,8,Fresuscitation but Mr Higgins said his
OL,9,Fwife "died right there on the pavement
OL,10,Fon a warm pleasant evening".
OL,12,FAfter offering condolences to Mrs
OL,13,FHiggins' family, the homeowner told
OL,14,Fthe inquest that there are several
OL,15,Flarge trees on the property and they
OL,16,Fall seemed healthy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
