CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775848268
OL,3,C'Tragic and devastating accident':
OL,4,CWoman killed by falling tree branch
OL,6,FHe said a tree surgeon had been called
OL,7,Fat one point, as he wanted a few of
OL,8,Fthe trees trimming to let in more
OL,9,Fnatural light, but the work had not
OL,10,Fended up happening as questions had
OL,11,Fbeen raised about whether it was in a
OL,12,Fconservation area. It was confirmed in
OL,13,Fcourt it was not.
OL,15,FThe court also heard from a senior
OL,16,Ftree surgeon who said the site from
OL,17,Fwhere the branch had fallen had
OL,18,Fsuffered "significant decay" when he
OL,19,Finspected it following the tragedy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
