OL,3,C'Tragic and devastating accident':
OL,4,CWoman killed by falling tree branch
OL,6,FHe told the court it had been
OL,7,F"inappropriately topped" more than 15
OL,8,Fyears ago - before the current owners
OL,9,Fmoved in - and he added it had
OL,10,Faggressive fungus.
OL,12,FA witness to the incident previously
OL,13,Fsaid" "The tree just snapped, it was a
OL,14,Fbig branch and just fell. A woman was
OL,15,Fwalking underneath. The weather was a
OL,16,Fbit windy but not strong."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
