OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775848268
OL,3,C'Tragic and devastating accident':
OL,4,CWoman killed by falling tree branch
OL,6,FCoroner Jessica Swift concluded on
OL,7,FFriday 10 April that the incident was
OL,8,F"nothing short of a tragic and
OL,9,Fdevastating accident" and told the
OL,10,Fcourt that the purpose of the inquest
OL,11,Fwas to establish how Mrs Higgins died,
OL,12,Frather than attribute blame.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
